<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 Error - Page Not Found</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 100px auto;
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }
        a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>404 Error - Page Not Found</h1>
        <p>Oops! It looks like the page you're trying to reach doesn't exist.</p>
        <p>You can <a href="/">return to the homepage</a> or try searching.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>